Command	Description
git stash	Save staged + unstaged changes
git stash -u	Also stash untracked files
git stash list	Show all stashes
git stash apply	Reapply latest stash (keep it)
git stash pop	Reapply latest stash (remove it)
git stash drop stash@{n}	Delete a specific stash
git stash clear	Delete all stashes
git stash push -m "msg"	Save stash with message
git stash branch <branch>	Create a branch from a stash



Command	What it does
git stash	Save tracked changes and clean working directory
git stash -u	Also include untracked files
git stash list	Show saved stashes
git stash apply	Reapply last stash, keep it
git stash pop	Reapply last stash, remove it
git stash drop	Delete one stash
git stash clear	Delete all stashes